languages.text: "Положительная оценка принята к сведению. Выражаю одобрительное удивление, что единица Кибелла, состоящая из ущербной плоти, также вернулась к функционированию".

languages.text: «Su valoración positiva queda registrada. Expreso una sorpresa aprobadora al ver que la unidad Kibellah, compuesta de carne imperfecta, también ha recuperado toda su funcionalidad».
languages.original_text: "Your positive assessment has been noted. I express approbative surprise that the unit Kibellah, composed of flawed flesh, has also been restored to functionality."

languages.text: 「その肯定的な評価は注目に値しますね。血管を持つ肉で構成されたユニットのキベラが機能を回復していることに対しても、称賛と驚きを表明します」
languages.original_text: "Your positive assessment has been noted. I express approbative surprise that the unit Kibellah, composed of flawed flesh, has also been restored to functionality."

languages.text: “已经将你的积极评价记录在案。尽管绮贝菈这个单位由有缺陷的肉体构成，但这个单位也同样恢复了功能性，我在此致以惊讶与赞赏。”
languages.original_text: "Your positive assessment has been noted. I express approbative surprise that the unit Kibellah, composed of flawed flesh, has also been restored to functionality."

languages.text: "Eure positive Beurteilung wurde notiert. Ich bin ausgesprochen überrascht, dass die aus makelbehaftetem Fleisch bestehende Einheit Kibellah wieder voll funktionsfähig ist."
languages.original_text: "Your positive assessment has been noted. I express approbative surprise that the unit Kibellah, composed of flawed flesh, has also been restored to functionality."

languages.text: « Votre évaluation positive est notée. Je m'étonne que l'unité Kibellah, pourtant composée de chair défectueuse, ait également été remise en état de marche. »
